OL,3,CPrison guard stabbed at high-security
OL,4,Cjail with 'extremely dangerous'
OL,5,Ccriminals
OL,7,FA prison officer has been stabbed by
OL,8,Fan inmate at a high-security prison,
OL,9,Fthe UK's prison service has confirmed.
OL,11,FPolice are investigating the attack,
OL,12,Fwhich happened this morning (30 May)
OL,13,Fat HMP Long Lartin near Evesham,
OL,14,FWorcestershire.
OL,16,FThe 25-year-old male guard was
OL,17,Fairlifted to hospital with serious
OL,18,Finjuries. He is said to be in a stable
OL,19,Fcondition.
