OL,7,FPolice said the inmate remains within
OL,8,Fthe prison and a weapon has been
OL,9,Frecovered.
OL,11,FA Prison Service spokesperson added:
OL,12,F"We will not tolerate assaults on
OL,13,Fhardworking staff and will always push
OL,14,Ffor the strongest punishments against
OL,15,Fperpetrators."
OL,17,FLong Lartin is a Category A men's
OL,18,Fprison, where more than two-thirds of
OL,19,Finmates are serving life sentences
OL,20,Fwith the rest serving terms of ten
OL,21,Fyears or more.
