OL,7,FDuring an inspection last September,
OL,8,Fthe prison's watchdog raised concerns
OL,9,Fabout gangs using drones to smuggle in
OL,10,Fdrugs, mobile phones and weapons.
OL,12,FInspectors said in a report published
OL,13,Fin January: "large quantities of drugs
OL,14,Fand other illicit items were entering
OL,15,Fthe prison, especially on drones.
OL,16,FPhysical security and counter measures
OL,17,Fwere not robust enough".
