OL,7,FThe Chief Inspector of Prisons,
OL,8,FCharlie Taylor, said said at the time:
OL,9,F"It is highly alarming that the police
OL,10,Fand prison service have, in effect
OL,11,Fceded the airspace above two high-
OL,12,Fsecurity prisons to organised crime
OL,13,Fgangs which are able to deliver
OL,14,Fcontraband to jails holding extremely
OL,15,Fdangerous prisoners including some who
OL,16,Fhave been designated as high-risk
OL,17,Fcategory A.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
