OL,5,Ccriminals
OL,7,F"The safety of staff, prisoners and
OL,8,Fultimately that of the public, is
OL,9,Fseriously compromised by the failure
OL,10,Fto tackle what has become a threat to
OL,11,Fnational security.
OL,13,F"The prison service, the police and
OL,14,Fother security services must urgently
OL,15,Fconfront organised gang activity and
OL,16,Freduce the supply of drugs and other
OL,17,Fillicit items which so clearly
OL,18,Fundermine every aspect of prison life."
